oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Marty Robbins
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: This recording features songs sung by Marty Robbins. Some of the songs recorder were written by Hank Snow and played by Marty Robbins. Hank Snow can be heard talking to Marty throughout the tape. The tape is dated May 31, 1955. This tape is the fourteenth of an unidentified number of tapes.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Marty Robbins; Hank Snow;
